  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3614231/" class="title-link">总共22个关键词，却没有正义和平等。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3614231"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/song1960/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1805066-25.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/song1960/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">宋歪麦</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-30"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-30 11:44:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3614231_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  总共22个关键词，却没有正义和平等。  居然敢叫政治哲学关键词。  只有三个词条算的上政治哲学关键词，人权，自由，民主。应用的材料不少，搭配很勉强。  从政治哲学看本书，只有《民主》稍微值得一看。自由一节次之。人权一节不堪入目。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3614231/#comments">(18回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 8没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
